{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/maxManosDescHeader.gif?t=1737197768\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/header1.png?t=1737197768\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/maxManosDescImage1.gif?t=1737197768\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Destroy as many shapes as you can within the given time. Some shapes may shoot projectiles upon destruction, sparking chaotic chain reactions. Break enough shapes, and you might even level up!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/header2.png?t=1737197768\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/maxManosDescImage2.gif?t=1737197768\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every destroyed shape drops shards - how convenient! Gather as many as possible because shards are the key to your progress as the game\u2019s currency.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/header3.png?t=1737197768\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/maxManosDescImage3.gif?t=1737197768\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use your shards to purchase a variety of upgrades from the shop. Empower Max Manos and unlock new abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/header4.png?t=1737197768\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/maxManosDescImage4.gif?t=1737197768\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With Max Manos upgraded, you\u2019ll destroy shapes more efficiently, collect even more shards, and buy even better upgrades. It's a circle of life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/header5.png?t=1737197768\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/maxManosDescImage5.gif?t=1737197768\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Now that Max Manos is an unstoppable force, let chaos reign supreme across the screen.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737197768","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/page.bg.jpg?t=1737197768","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/61dace0f27933c3041417d303cae7a239ef9da02/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737197768","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/61dace0f27933c3041417d303cae7a239ef9da02/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737197768","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Stats","id":15},{"description":"Steam Leaderboards","id":25}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/maxManosDescHeader.gif?t=1737197768\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/st